Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Style,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[OP]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.86,0:01:49.43,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇と遊ぶ星たちへ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.61,0:01:54.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛を歌い　飽きつくした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.31,0:01:58.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏を灯し　雛菊の
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.02,0:02:04.31,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢に寄り添う爪の痕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:12.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唇から唇へと伝い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:16.94,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その温もりはどこへ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:23.44,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辿り付くあてはないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:29.50,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたでなくちゃ　満たせない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:34.13,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私じゃなきゃ　許せなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:38.89,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから　私はこの足で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:41.25,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立ち上がれて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:43.65,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぞっとしたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:48.25,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飼い殺しなら　救われる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:52.98,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でも見事に　鍵は外れて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:03:03.89,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私はまるで　鳥籠を欲している狂う籠鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:11.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘を抱いた花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.86,0:01:49.43,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与黑暗游戏的星斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.61,0:01:54.09,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为爱咏唱　我已经厌倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.31,0:01:58.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点亮夏季的雏菊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.02,0:02:04.31,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴随梦境的爪痕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:12.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过双唇传递而来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:16.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份温存将何去何从
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:23.44,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没有可以前往的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:29.50,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是你　我得不到满足
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:34.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是我　是不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:38.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我能用自己的双脚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:41.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站立起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:43.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却感到心惊胆寒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:48.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果养我一生　我还可以得救
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:52.98,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是　锁却顺利打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:03:03.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宛如为渴求鸟笼而疯狂的笼中之鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:11.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀抱谎言的花

Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Style,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[ED]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.78,0:22:55.77,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見てて　ご覧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:23:01.42,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほら　満ちぬけた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:06.37,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溢れた傍から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.69,0:23:12.20,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消えて　抜け殻に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.04,0:23:22.19,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流されて　辿り付く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.73,0:23:28.08,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現　蕩ける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.75,0:23:34.19,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天この魂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.52,0:23:44.70,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢　紡いだ夢を　どうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.97,0:23:53.75,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その小指に絡めなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:58.07,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛んだ刺は
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.04,0:24:04.22,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一つ抜ける
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.93,0:24:09.21,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取る　抜ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.78,0:22:55.77,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请注意看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:23:01.42,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊　充满了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:06.37,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从溢出的一侧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.69,0:23:12.20,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐渐消失　变成了空壳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.04,0:23:22.19,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随波逐流　到达彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.73,0:23:28.08,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉醉于现实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.75,0:23:34.19,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.52,0:23:44.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦　编织的梦境　请看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.97,0:23:53.75,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请缠绕我的小指不放开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:58.07,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼痛的刺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.04,0:24:04.22,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一根被拔掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.93,0:24:09.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取出　拔掉

Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.08,0:00:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山河三岔路 别离之路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要保护的是自己 是他人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是常世的黑暗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是非对错无法补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.46,0:00:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有终结的深仇大恨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭转时空 打开大门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难报之怨 我为您报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执剑火天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云海御经
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.29,0:00:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 你们适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.90,0:00:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,则天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.98,0:00:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:01:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮入道也当次老师嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不当呢 我又不是当老师的料
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.32,0:01:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要为明天的试验做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.74,0:01:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来我也有事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤川变了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前在一个班的时候

Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要可乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 我今天有约会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我没钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢 汤川
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 3万
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤川 来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5点车站前见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会告诉班主任丹下老师的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会为难的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么为难的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说跌倒了 是在说谎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为难的是 我不想因为受伤而给大家添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您一定要说出去的话 我不会再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么不会再来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不来医务室了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校也不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后我会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤川吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲是银行职员 母亲是家庭主妇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个非常普通的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:04:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你这么一说 上课时他好像确实有点发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 以后我也会多注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想逆转形势 只有瞄准脸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用这个特制雪球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我要赢了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不觉得羞耻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我记着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要觉得丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都21了 还是这么光滑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的「猛」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大和猛的「猛」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 没问过父母
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 经常有人这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说和我的形象不符
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁志田的名字叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫晋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长得很像普通的「普」的那个晋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:06:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是大学生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大三 剑道系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有剑道系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是法律系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你将来要当律师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是检察官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检察官很适合你哦 仁志田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在那之前 要先通过司法考试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油的 你也要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能会剑道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想变强吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直像这样被人打却不能还手也行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 我从小就习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,习惯了也就没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要习惯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 所谓社会就是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方只能通过这种形式才能站在别人之上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 就随便他们去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是得了冠军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的不是结果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果是根据对手而定的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我指的不是这个 是自身的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还缺少什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我觉得已经很完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么完美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又强又聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长得也好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么我不受欢迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.96,0:09:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许大家觉得你可望不可即
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗 我可望不可即
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说男生可能不太合适
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这个倒不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,论外表的话 你要更胜一筹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 你长得很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是男的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦 真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 是男人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是男人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是男人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放春假的时候 陪我练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动后很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汗流进眼睛里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你擦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猛改变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.29,0:10:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然说要剑道器材的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈吓了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不向那个人送礼道谢 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然应该道谢了 不 必须要道谢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么没关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算送礼给他 他也不会接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁志田就是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么都是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:11:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朴实刚毅 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有两袖清风 少壮气锐什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像把这些成语集于一身的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 是个非常出色的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样的人 全世界只有他一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近变了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比以前帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是感冒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早退吧 去医院看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近 汤川猛怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤川吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不在一个班了 不过他好像很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说在学剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤川在学剑道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道什么时候开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.23,0:12:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新学期开始的时候已经在学了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那没再受到欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直看着黑烟 你不腻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不腻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 可以拜托您吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在一边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以现在的年轻人来看 是个不错的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且长得也很帅 很大气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 还比不上我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晕车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有风吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 真辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个法律学校的能力测验难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起能力测验 问题在那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁志田没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁帮我拧一下背上的发条
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.56,0:14:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开车了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚的是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被这个刺中的话当然疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很疼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站是和田原神社入口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公共汽车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所愿 我把你的头弄圆了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}下一站是4丁目路口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下站要下车了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下站停车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 有些地方还没剪干净
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 跟我到组里来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你剃干净
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是车钱 不用找了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开车了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在这里分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介意什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是没办法的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会看不起我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不起我也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 请听我解释一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.26,0:17:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你在一旁 我不能做危险的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能把你牵扯进去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:17:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一目连
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.58,0:18:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的想报怨 就解开这根红线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开红线 你就和我正式结下了契约
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨的人会当即被冲入地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是报怨后 你自身也要付出代价
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人必害己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约生效后 你的灵魂也会堕入地狱的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 那是你死后的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法前往极乐净土
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂会饱受痛苦 永远徘徊于地狱中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:19:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 必须有人来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道错的不只是他一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正应该下地狱的也许是其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那些人和我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我 和我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的怨恨 我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 是我不对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.06,0:20:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 可以给我机会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.03,0:20:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么机会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补偿的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为检察官 然后弥补自己的过错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我从小的梦想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.87,0:20:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为检察官 惩罚恶人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:20:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这个 我一直努力至今
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这么说了哦 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被黑暗迷惑的悲哀之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.09,0:21:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害他人 贬低他人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于罪孽中的罪恶灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死一次试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那辆公共汽车上的人都同罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.60,0:21:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 为什么只有我一个 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怨恨 我会把它冲入地狱的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.05,0:21:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不说你也知道吧 不许打小报告哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:21:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
